wikipedia_page.main: Paul Leon Miller McCallum (born 28 July 1993) is an English professional footballer who plays as a striker for Dagenham & Redbridge. He has previously played for clubs including West Ham United, AFC Wimbledon, Leyton Orient, Hearts and Portsmouth.
